abstract: >
  Cumulative public Deep Origin Theory checkpoint that preserves the prior J2C
  result release files as visible sibling files and adds the DO-K1 conditional
  galactic-engine public pre-execution lock. The checkpoint freezes the exact
  DO-K1 local field equation, global I0 boundary-condition policy, same-metric
  rotation/lensing map, future NGC0247 exposed sign-topology challenge contract,
  and comparator prelock before any galaxy execution. It claims no galaxy
  result, no MOND/QUMOND family defeat, no SPARC fit, no origin derivation for
  I0, and no final cosmic closure.
